[div class=p 
	"To share input files, use 
	[a class=intlink href=/Userfiles 
		"User movies
	]a
	". It has a 4 MB size limit, but you can upload compressed input files if your movie is bigger than that. Alternatively, you can use 
	[a href=http://dehacked.2y.net/microstorage.php rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"Microstorage
	]a
	". It has a 2 MB size limit, so if your input file is bigger, compress it with GZip. Bear in mind that not all site-submittable formats are supported by Microstorage.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"For embedded images (you may or may not need this), use 
	[a href=http://imgur.com/ rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"Imgur
	]a
	".
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"For code files, use 
	[a href=http://pastebin.com/ rel=noopener external nofollow 
